Todays hyperfixations apparently: Pokémon fans and Violet Evergarden.

All apologies.

I still liked the movie, but that’s because I didn’t read their interactions as romantic. But like, towards the end you could tell that they were trying to push it that way and I was like?? Why? But also, I hated the end of the movie for many reasons💀 yet the show is a 10/10!

I like having the cries in game, and the name cries in anime. Am I gonna shove this down peoples throats? No. At the end of the day I could not give a crap what you think is the end all be all of Pokémon cries. I’m just amazed at how easily Pokémon fans foam at the mouth lol 💀
I don’t care what your preference is; I’m just saying, arguing that you’re “correct” in this argument is stupid because it’s all based on preference and opinion on FICTIONAL monsters.
